<doc f='halide/llvm-install/include/llvm/IR/DiagnosticInfo.h' l='771'>/// \p PassName is the name of the pass emitting this diagnostic. If this name
  /// matches the regular expression given in -Rpass-analysis=, then the
  /// diagnostic will be emitted. \p RemarkName is a textual identifier for the
  /// remark (single-word, camel-case). \p Loc is the debug location and \p
  /// CodeRegion is the region that the optimization operates on (currently only
  /// block is supported).</doc>
